lead_paragraph: Michael Phelps gifted himself an early birthday present by winning the 200 meters butterfly at the U.S. Olympic swim trials on Wednesday to punch his ticket to the Rio Summer Games.

headline.main: Phelps on Way to Rio After Olympic Trials Win
